      <p>where <italic>p</italic><sub><italic>ri</italic></sub> is the prevalence for population <italic>i</italic> in region <italic>r</italic>, <inline-formula id="IEq4"><alternatives><tex-math id="M13">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
