      <p>Despite the large number of individual calculations in this algorithm, since it does not require the model itself to be rerun, it is quite computationally efficient. For example, in the Ukraine case study (<italic>N</italic>=3 and <italic>K</italic>=2000), this algorithm takes several seconds to run on a standard laptop, compared with roughly an hour to compute the three BOCs.</p>
